0.1.8.name: wordpress/fotomoto
0.1.8.description: Fotomoto allows you to quickly and easily turn your photoblog into a fully featured e-commerce store. Sign up at http://www.fotomoto.com to receive your unique key and use it to activate the plugin and your pictures and photos will automatically have a buy me button under each of them. This plugin adds the required javascript for enabling the Fotomoto store on all pages.
